The order of 7 parameters of the USER's function
COMPONENTS of the INITIAL DISPLACEMENT
at time T, at point X,Y,Z, 
for the PLSVO of type number NO_TYPE_OBJECT
(1:POINT, 2:LINE, 3:SURFACE, 4:VOLUME, 5:OBJECT )
the directory number NO_OBJECT
NCOMP number of the INITIAL DISPLACEMENT component
must be

INIT_DISPL( T, X, Y, Z, NO_TYPE_OBJET, NO_OBJET, NCOMP ) 

and be programmed with respect to LU grammar
(cf documentation and examples of the debut menu)

All these parameters will be initialized during its call.
These parameters can be used or not, but have to be present
in the definition of the function INIT_DISPL.
 
EXAMPLE:
deffunc init_displact( t, x, y, z, no_type_objet, material, nc ) ;
if    nc=1
then  init_displact=0.0;
else  if    nc=2
      then init_displact=0.001;
      else init_displact=0.003;
      endif;  
endif;
endfunc; 

Remark: The LU function nuobjt( p1, p2 ) gives the number of
        the PLSVO of type p1 with the name p2.
